org.cloudgraph.store.key

Enum GraphMetaKey

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<GraphMetaKey>
      • org.cloudgraph.store.key.GraphMetaKey
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<GraphMetaKey>, MetaKey

    public enum GraphMetaKey
extends java.lang.Enum<GraphMetaKey>
implements MetaKey
    Enumeration based qualifier or code-set used to describe a graph/row.

    The enumeration name is referenced directly in source code, and the underlying code is used as the actual physical column qualifier. The allows the source to remain more readable while allowing more terse physical qualifiers or column keys.
    Since:
    1.0.0
    Author:
    Scott Cinnamond
